.TH "intel_huc_auth" 9 "intel_huc_auth" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
intel_huc_auth \- Authenticate HuC uCode
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" intel_huc_auth
.BI "(struct intel_huc *huc "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "huc" 12
intel_huc structure
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Called after HuC and GuC firmware loading during \fBintel_uc_init_hw\fP.

This function invokes the GuC action to authenticate the HuC firmware,
passing the offset of the RSA signature to \fBintel_guc_auth_huc\fP. It then
waits for up to 50ms for firmware verification ACK.
